         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">12/10/84 ¶  ¶ While looking through a few plants today, respected Mr Holtze, I find that your No. 396 ¶  is  ¶ Gossypium flaviflorum ¶ . This lovely species has only been known from the Glenelg River ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">84.10.12</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Maurice Holtze</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">GRG 19/391, State Records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">12/10/84</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Beim Durchsehen einiger Pflanzen am heutigen Tage, geehrter Herr Holtze, finde ich, dass Ihr 396 = <name key="Gossypium%20flaviflorum">Gossypium flaviflorum</name> ist. Diese schöne Art war bisher nur von einem Platz am Glenelg Fluss bekannt, u. die Frucht ist noch nirgend gesammelt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoffentlich höre ich bald wieder von Ihnen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundlichst grüssend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Haben Sie nie von den Farnbäumen gehört, die in der Nähe des Glenelg Flusses vorkommen sollen?</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">12/10/84</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>While looking through a few plants today, respected Mr Holtze, I find that your No. 396<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to M. Holtze, August 1884 (in this edition as 84-08-00), where M was less definite in identifying the specimen as <seg style="font-style: italic; ">G. flaviflorum</seg>.</p>
               </note> is <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Gossypium%20flaviflorum">Gossypium flaviflorum</name>
               </seg>. This lovely species has only been known from the Glenelg River<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">i.e. Glenelg River, WA.</p>
               </note> so far, and no fruit has been collected of it anywhere.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope to hear from you soon.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With most friendly greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Have you never heard of the tree ferns that are said to grow in the vicinity of the Glenelg River?</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Gossypium%20flaviflorum">Gossypium flaviflorum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
